    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out or not assessed at MRL 2. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied at all five COU operating points.",
